data.description: Townhome, with 2 Bedroom, each with bathrooms, upstairs laundry with washer & dryer.  Open floor plan, Kitchen has pantry and lots of counter space and includes all kitchen appliances.  Fresh paint and new carpet.  Gas Log Fireplace with built in bookcase in Living Room. HOA includes yard maintenance, use of Riverwood pools & fitness center and golf. Neighborhood daycare, elementary & middle schools. Close to shopping, doctors office walking trails.
